reviewText: Just received my copy in the mail yesterday. I found out about Shpongle from OZORA. The ONLY place to purchase this title now is from Twisted Music (UK). It's NOT NTSC............ Shipping was 1 pound airmailed to me in the USA. I received my copy within 10 days. I played my Shpongle through a muti-media computer (uses HDMI). BOTH the audio and video are top notch. This concert is one of a kind and most excellent.

reviewText: Shpongle is a phenomenal act, so much so that I was propelled to prostitute myself in order to be able to scrounge up the $21,064 necessary to purchase this DVD.To the uninitiated, Shpongle occupies a lofty spot atop the the glitchcore/electronic/tripjizz/spankgloop/quasitrance/chill/shtoinkrama realm and their music can transcend, hallucinate and fellate the listener in innumerable ways, each better than the last.If you buy one $21,064 DVD this year, make it this one.
Title: N/A

reviewText: I'm watching the DVD for the first time and it is everything I hoped it would be minus one thing.  The audio is engineered in stereo and not 5.1 which is the only reason I knocked a star off.  It still sounds great but it would have been that much better in digital 5.1.  Buy this, you'll love it!
summary: Do you love Shpongle?  You will love this!
